{"tid":2273284,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"TG酒谷招募谷友","createTime":"2020-11-05T15:20:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T09:33:57.000Z","uid":236788,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2cd5070af9cc489e41d607b4fbfefa83a515f363","tid":2273284,"uid":236788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T15:20:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />重點招募<span class=\"x-large\">鐵腳</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然武肺來襲，<br />\n但係都熄滅唔到我地飲酒嘅心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大有大搞，細有細搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n志在飲得開心，吹得暢快。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">溫馨提示</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n谷中情侶多<br />\n狗公小心衝錯人，<br />\n娘娘小心惹錯火。<br />\n<br />\n誠邀<span class=\"gold\">講求衛生</span><span class=\"pink\">酒品好</span><span class=\"teal\">有禮貌</span>嘅正常人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAE6t7s6QNmtwMF7mrw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAE6t7s6QNmtwMF7mrw&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8lNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=f373139e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAE6t7s6QNmtwMF7mrw</a>"},{"pid":"862a74519238210ca60a9d81d97c934e89a2b22a","tid":2273284,"uid":6238,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T08:58:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"511ecbcd43b4d6f8dc6d35203c9496fe3e3e5dbf","tid":2273284,"uid":6238,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T02:42:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2079dbae997fad960c41d5ea4bc43db27352b7fb","tid":2273284,"uid":6238,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:15:50.000Z","